===UEFA Nations League===
England have competed in the [[UEFA Nations League]] since its inaugural season in 2018–19, when they qualified for the [[2019 UEFA Nations League Finals|2019 finals]] and finished third overall. To date, this is their only appearance in the finals and their best performance in the competition.

